  pandas
  (<xref alt="The pandas development team, 2026" rid="ref-The_pandas_development_team_pandas-dev_pandas_Pandas" ref-type="bibr">The
  pandas development team, 2026</xref>), Polars
  (<xref alt="Polars Contributors, 2024" rid="ref-polars2024" ref-type="bibr">Polars
